#moduleImport
import turtle

#userInput
locationX = int(input("Please enter x value for center of target - "))
locationY = int(input("Please enter y value for center of target - "))
centDiameter = float(input("please enter desired diameter of center ring - "))

#variableConversion
xPos = abs(locationX)
yPos = abs(locationY)
Radius = centDiameter / 2

#outermostRing

#definingLocation
yPos += 4 * Radius

#drawingRing
turtle.penup()
turtle.goto(xPos

locationX = int(input("Please enter x value for center of target - "))
locationY = int(input("Please enter y value for center of target - "))
centDiameter = float(input("please enter desired diameter of center ring - "))

yPos = abs(locationY)
Radius = centDiameter / 2

#outermostRing

#definingLocation
yPos += 4 * Radius

#drawingRing
turtle.penup()
turtle.goto(xPos
